headline.main: EXILED ARAB MUFTI TURNS UP IN ROME; Italians Proclaim Plan for Pro-Axis Moslem Revolt in the Middle East

lead_paragraph: ROME, Oct. 27 -- Haj Amin el Husseini, exiled Mufti of Jerusalem and chief foe of Britain in the Arab world, is in Rome today after what is described as an adventurous flight by plane from the Middle East.
abstract: el Husseine arrives, Rome; Itals proclaim plan for pro-Axis Moslem revolt In Middle East
